Snippet: topper-quote.liquid
Purpose: Displays a "Request a Quote" button and modal form for truck parts, with separate dropdowns for truck makes and models, and a two-column layout for specified field pairs on tablet and wider screens.
Usage: Included in product template.
Dependencies: Requires jQuery and Bootstrap for modal functionality.
Notes: Sends product_id instead of variant_id. Uses server URL https://custom-shopify.onrender.com. Validates phone, VIN, and address fields. Layout on tablet and wider: First Name | Last Name, Email | Phone Number, Country | State, Vehicle Year | VIN Number in two columns; Address, Vehicle Make, Vehicle Model, Message in single columns. Vehicle Model is dependent on Vehicle Make.
